ActOther Than Statutory Authority
PrecisAppointment of LILIAN CHATTERJEE to be High Commissioner for Canada in Barbados; WENDY DRUKIER to be Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Spain, with concurrent accreditation as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Principality of Andorra, with residence in Madrid; ALAIN GENDRON to be Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Belgium; ANNICK GOULET to be Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Bulgaria, with residence in Bucharest; BENOÎT-PIERRE LARAMÉE to be Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Democratic Republic of the Congo; and ISABELLE VALOIS to be Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Eastern Republic of Uruguay.
